  "title": "Center Care Taker",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a center care taker for PlayFACTO School at Bedok Reservoir (Mon-Fri, 11am-5.30pm)</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of the premise</li><li>Prepare snacks and heat up meals for children (no cooking required)</li><li>Wash plates and utensils</li><li>Provide basic care for students</li><li>Any ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Working Hours</strong></p><p>Mon - Fri, 11am - 5.30am</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Salary</strong></p><p>$1,100 - $1,300</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested personnel, send your resume by applying for this role or WhatsApp to 81128546.</p><p><br /></p><p>We seek your understanding that only shortlisted candidates would be contacted.</p>",
